---
title: Chinese Pork & Veggie Stir-Fry with Sesame Cauliflower Rice & Crispy Shallots
description: This dish is an irresistible combination of Asian greens, tasty pork and sesame-studded cauliflower rice, all with the feel-good factor of a carb-smart rice substitute and cooking a filling meal from scratch. The best part is the addition of crispy shallots to make it super satisfying.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/low-carb-chinese-pork-veggie-stir-fry-fc95ae7a.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/chinese-pork-veggie-stir-fry-60ab17c4b9699f656e29f84e-c17369b3.pdf
